wn.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇多左幾次之後我覺得果幕即刻停戰係因為最後batman發現superman同佢一樣都係人 係死前一刻都想救家人 不過無再加以解釋下呢個原因真係拍得好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />第一次睇心諗做乜撚野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6852fc57d86c61688e594ec1f56d055bc9a1cba7","tid":137004,"uid":11914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T09:08:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講得出bvs最差上年應該睇唔夠十套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係最差， 但一定係最失望"},{"pid":"d31f24523f9a246262547977df5801c5b3b69073","tid":137004,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T09:58:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講得出bvs最差上年應該睇唔夠十套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係最差， 但一定係最失望</blockquote><br />\nGolden raspberry 果d獎都係worst乜乜乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358ab627773727e7d1a356cceb447dfe7394ce8d","tid":137004,"uid":10392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:40:13.000Z","msg":"Dc又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ef9d15e734039924ce9c6fe21fbaeea3045466","tid":137004,"uid":41309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:45:44.000Z","msg":"金草梅獎睇野唔夠深度唔夠dark"}]}